<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> "Annika Moscati" .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> "Bincy Veena" .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> "Peter Johansson" .
