<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A modular semantic framework for role-, attribute-, relationship-, and\n         purpose-based access control over Digital Product Passport data,\n         aligned with ESPR, GDPR, and ODRL 2.2."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "DPP Access Control Ontology Module"@en .
