<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#appliedPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#appliedPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessDecision> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#appliedPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessPolicy> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#appliedPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The AccessPolicy (or policies) that were evaluated to produce\n         this decision."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#appliedPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "applied policy"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#appliesToRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#appliesToRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
