<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#appliesToRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessPolicy> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#appliesToRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Role> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#appliesToRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Role to which this AccessPolicy is addressed."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#appliesToRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "applies to role"@en .
# 
