<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#belongsToModule> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#belongsToModule> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#DPPResource> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#belongsToModule> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/data-categories#DataCategory> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/data-categories#DataCategory> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#belongsToModule> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The ESPR-defined data category (DPP module) that contains this resource."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#belongsToModule> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "belongs to module"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decidesOn
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decidesOn> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decidesOn> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decidesOn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessDecision> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decidesOn> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessRequest> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decidesOn> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Links this AccessDecision to the AccessRequest it resolves."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decidesOn> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "decides on"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedBy
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Delegation> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Principal> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Principal who grants delegated access rights."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "delegated by"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedTo
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Delegation> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Principal> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Principal who receives delegated access rights."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegatedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "delegated to"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversAction
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversAction> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversAction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Delegation> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversAction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/Action> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/Action> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversAction> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The action(s) the delegatee is authorised to perform."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversAction> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "delegation covers action"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversResource
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversResource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Delegation> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#DPPResource> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The DPP resource(s) over which delegated rights are granted."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationCoversResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "delegation covers resource"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasAttributeConstraint
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasAttributeConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasAttributeConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessPolicy> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasAttributeConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AttributeConstraint> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasAttributeConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Links an AccessPolicy to one or more AttributeConstraints that\n         must all be satisfied for the policy's permissions to activate."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasAttributeConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "has attribute constraint"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Principal> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Role> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Assigns a single Access Control Role to a Principal."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#hasRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "has role"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#ownedBy
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#ownedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#ownedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#ownedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#DPPResource> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#ownedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Principal> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#ownedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Principal who is the authoritative data owner of this\n         DPP resource and may grant or revoke access."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#ownedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "owned by"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyOwner
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyOwner> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyOwner> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyOwner> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessPolicy> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyOwner> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Principal> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyOwner> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Principal responsible for the lifecycle of this policy."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyOwner> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "policy owner"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestContext
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestContext> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessRequest> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessContext> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestContext> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Environmental or situational metadata that conditions the evaluation\n         of this access request."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestContext> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "request context"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedAction
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedAction> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedAction> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedAction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessRequest> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedAction> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/Action> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedAction> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The CRUD action the Principal intends to perform."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedAction> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "requested action"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedBy
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessRequest> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Principal> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Links an AccessRequest to the Principal who submitted it."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "requested by"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedResource
