<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedResource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessRequest> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#DPPResource> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The DPP resource the Principal intends to access."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestedResource> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "requested resource"@en .
