# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidFrom
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#TemporalContext> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The UTC date-time from which this temporal access window opens."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "access valid from"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidUntil
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#TemporalContext> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The UTC date-time at which this temporal access window closes."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#accessValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "access valid until"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#certificationIsValid
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#certificationIsValid> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
