<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#certificationIsValid> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#CertificationContext> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#certificationIsValid> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#certificationIsValid> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "True if the referenced certification is currently valid and in good standing."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#certificationIsValid> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "certification is valid"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#certificationScheme
