<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#certificationScheme> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The name or identifier of the certification scheme."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#certificationScheme> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "certification scheme"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#conflictResolutionApplied
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#conflictResolutionApplied> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#conflictResolutionApplied> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessDecision> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#conflictResolutionApplied> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#conflictResolutionApplied> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "True if a deny-overrides conflict resolution strategy was\n         invoked during this decision evaluation."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#conflictResolutionApplied> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "conflict resolution applied"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintAttribute
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintAttribute> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
