<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintAttribute> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AttributeConstraint> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintAttribute> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintAttribute> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The name of the attribute being constrained."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintAttribute> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "constraint attribute"@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintAttribute> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "E.g., trustAssuranceLevel, resourceSensitivity, certificationIsValid."@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintOperator
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintOperator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintOperator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintOperator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AttributeConstraint> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintOperator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintOperator> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The comparison operator applied to the attribute value."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintOperator> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "constraint operator"@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintOperator> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Allowed values: EQ, NEQ, GT, LT, GTE, LTE, IN."@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintValue
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintValue> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintValue> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AttributeConstraint> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintValue> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The value against which the attribute is compared."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#constraintValue> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "constraint value"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionOutcome
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionOutcome> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionOutcome> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionOutcome> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessDecision> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionOutcome> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionOutcome> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The result of evaluating the access request."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionOutcome> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "decision outcome"@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionOutcome> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Allowed values: GRANT, DENY, DELEGATE, PENDING."@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionTimestamp
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessDecision> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The UTC date-time at which the access decision was recorded."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#decisionTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "decision timestamp"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#declaredPurpose
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#declaredPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#declaredPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#declaredPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#PurposeContext> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#declaredPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#declaredPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A textual description of the purpose for which data access is requested."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#declaredPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "declared purpose"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationDepth
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationDepth> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationDepth> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationDepth> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Delegation> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationDepth> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationDepth> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The number of sub-delegation hops permitted from this delegation."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationDepth> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "delegation depth"@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationDepth> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Maximum allowed value is 1. Sub-delegation is prohibited by policy."@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationIsActive
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationIsActive> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationIsActive> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationIsActive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Delegation> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationIsActive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationIsActive> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "True if this delegation is currently within its valid time window\n         and has not been revoked."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationIsActive> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "delegation is active"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidFrom
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Delegation> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The UTC date-time from which the delegation is active."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "delegation valid from"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidUntil
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Delegation> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The UTC date-time at which the delegation expires."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#delegationValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "delegation valid until"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#jurisdictionCode
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#jurisdictionCode> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#jurisdictionCode> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#jurisdictionCode> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#GeographicContext> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#jurisdictionCode> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#jurisdictionCode> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The jurisdiction in which this access constraint applies."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#jurisdictionCode> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "jurisdiction code"@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#jurisdictionCode> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 country code, or the literals EU or EEA."@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#permittedPurpose
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#permittedPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#permittedPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessPolicy> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#permittedPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#permittedPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A purpose code that an access request must declare to activate\n         this policy's permissions."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#permittedPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "permitted purpose"@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#permittedPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Must be one of the purpose codes defined in PurposeContextShape:\n         MAINTENANCE, COMPLIANCE_AUDIT, RECYCLING_PROCESSING,\n         MARKET_SURVEILLANCE, CUSTOMS_INSPECTION, CONSUMER_INFORMATION,\n         RESEARCH_DEVELOPMENT, SUPPLY_CHAIN_DUE_DILIGENCE."@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidFrom
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessPolicy> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The UTC date-time from which this policy is active."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "policy valid from"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidUntil
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessPolicy> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The UTC date-time after which this policy expires."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#policyValidUntil> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "policy valid until"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestTimestamp
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#AccessRequest> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The UTC date-time at which the AccessRequest was submitted."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#requestTimestamp> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "request timestamp"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#resourceSensitivity
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#resourceSensitivity> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#resourceSensitivity> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
